{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "293964ee-86a7-49d2-8beb-f1645a9d1881", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/293964ee-86a7-49d2-8beb-f1645a9d1881@1.pkg/1772602423210/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602423672", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/293964ee-86a7-49d2-8beb-f1645a9d1881@1.pkg/1772602423210/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602423672"}, "identifier": "293964ee-86a7-49d2-8beb-f1645a9d1881", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>“未选择的路”强调的是对自己人生道路的选择要慎重，诗中并没有体现诗人彷徨和苦闷的情绪。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>1.下列对本课两首诗歌的理解分析不正确的一项是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "1.下列对本课两首诗歌的理解分析不正确的一项是（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/293964ee-86a7-49d2-8beb-f1645a9d1881@1.pkg/item.json?v=1753973067570", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>《假如生活欺骗了你》一诗以劝说的口吻、和缓的语气，鼓励人们相信生活，相信未来。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>《未选择的路》，作者借写自然界的道路来表达对人生之路的思考，运用了象征的手法。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>《假如生活欺骗了你》诗句清新流畅，热烈深沉，有丰富的人情味和哲理意味，可以让人从中感受到诗人真诚博大的情怀和坚强乐观的心态。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>《未选择的路》中，“未选择的路”说明了诗人对自己的人生道路充满彷徨和苦闷。</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>1.下列对本课两首诗歌的理解分析不正确的一项是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5036342747", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5136342961", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342961", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "293964ee-86a7-49d2-8beb-f1645a9d1881", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "1.下列对本课两首诗歌的理解分析不正确的一项是（   ）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>1.下列对本课两首诗歌的理解分析不正确的一项是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/293964ee-86a7-49d2-8beb-f1645a9d1881@1.pkg/1772602423210/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602423672", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/293964